{"title":"Salsa Updates the EXP Bike Bag Line with Panniers, Saddle Bags, and More","link":"https://theradavist.com/salsa-exp-bags-panniers-saddle-frame-bags/","date":1720746521000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20240322_SAL_Cutthroat_Teal_01.jpg?fit=1200,1333&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20240322_SAL_Cutthroat_Teal_01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20240322_SAL_Cutthroat_Teal_01.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20240322_SAL_Cutthroat_Teal_01.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/20240322_SAL_Cutthroat_Teal_01.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/bicycle+touring/\" target=\"_blank\">Adventure by Bike</a> just got easier with three all-new <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/Salsa+Cycles/\" target=\"_blank\">Salsa Cycles</a> EXP Series bike bags. The panniers, frame and saddle bags are designed to fit more bikes and more adventures into your life, these bags will see you and your gear through bikepacking races, quick <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/Overnighter/\" target=\"_blank\">sub-24-hour overnighters</a>, and ends-of-the-Earth bike tours alike. Read on for a look at these three new bags.</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"683\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0364.jpg?fit=1200,683&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0364.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0364.jpg?resize=1200,410&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0364.jpg?resize=768,262&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0364.jpg?resize=1536,525&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img width=\"2000\" height=\"1337\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0366-05.jpg?fit=1200,1337&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0366-05.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0366-05.jpg?resize=1200,802&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0366-05.jpg?resize=768,513&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0366-05.jpg?resize=1536,1027&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/gear/exp-series-cholla-half-frame-bag\" target=\"_blank\">The Cholla Frame Bag</a></h3>\n<p>A versatile half-frame bag with inclusive fit on a wider range of Salsa frames and rider sizes. Itâ€™s perfect for stowing ride essentials on a light-and-fast Adventure by Bike on gravel, dirt, and pavement.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Price $90 USD</li>\n<li>Direct-mount capable with compatible Salsa frames</li>\n<li>Fits a wide range of non-Salsa frames with included straps</li>\n<li>Inclusive fit with extended size range (six sizes)</li>\n<li>1000D Cordura nylon body with 400D nylon lining</li>\n<li>Durable molded-tooth zippers</li>\n<li>Cut-and-sewn construction</li>\n<li>Drive-side access with non-drive-side slash pocket</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1066\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0372-01.jpg?fit=1200,1066&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0372-01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0372-01.jpg?resize=1200,640&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0372-01.jpg?resize=768,409&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0372-01.jpg?resize=1536,819&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1514\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0488-01.jpg?fit=1200,1514&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0488-01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0488-01.jpg?resize=1200,908&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0488-01.jpg?resize=768,581&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0488-01.jpg?resize=1536,1163&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/gear/exp-series-saguaro-seat-bag\" target=\"_blank\">The Saguaro Seat Bag</a> and <a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/gear/exp-series-saguaro-dry-bag\" target=\"_blank\">Dry Bags</a></h3>\n<p>A quick-loading, easy to use, and stable over the roughest terrain. Price $120 (md), $140 (lg) USD. The waterproof dry bag keeps gear safe through the worst weather conditions. Price $50 (md, 9L), $55 (lg, 14L) USD.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Holster-style with removable dry bag for easy packing</li>\n<li>Welded waterproof dry bag with air purge valve</li>\n<li>Four-point connection to saddle rails for increased stability</li>\n<li>Dropper post-compatible</li>\n<li>Fits on almost any bike</li>\n<li>Two sizes: Medium (9 liters) and Large (14 liters)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2407\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370.jpg?fit=1200,2407&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370.jpg?resize=1200,1444&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370.jpg?resize=768,924&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370.jpg?resize=1276,1536&amp;quality=75 1276w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370.jpg?resize=1702,2048&amp;quality=75 1702w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1788\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-02.jpg?fit=1200,1788&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-02.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-02.jpg?resize=1200,1073&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-02.jpg?resize=768,687&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-02.jpg?resize=1536,1373&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2539\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-01.jpg?fit=1200,2539&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-01.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-01.jpg?resize=1200,1523&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-01.jpg?resize=768,975&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-01.jpg?resize=1210,1536&amp;quality=75 1210w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/07/BG0370-01.jpg?resize=1613,2048&amp;quality=75 1613w\" /></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/gear/exp-series-agave-pannier\" target=\"_blank\">The Agave Pannier</a></h3>\n<p>Built for safe storage on pavement and gravel adventure rides with rattle and hassle-free attachment and a completely waterproof construction. Panniers are still the most stable way to carry your goods on and off-road.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Price $90 USD</li>\n<li>Rixen and Kaul hardware for secure rack attachment</li>\n<li>Welded construction with waterproof materials</li>\n<li>Mesh front pocket and reflective side patches</li>\n<li>Designed to avoid heel strike</li>\n<li>Compatible with most racks</li>\n<li>12.5 liter capacity</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check out the full EXP line at <a href=\"https://www.salsacycles.com/gear/accessories\" target=\"_blank\">Salsa</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/salsa-exp-bags-panniers-saddle-frame-bags/\">Salsa Updates the EXP Bike Bag Line with Panniers, Saddle Bags, and More</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ccb222a1e0188371226f301cebc75383d86206c94daec1dedc11c3af21b9227d","category":"Cycling"}